213
00:17:22,450 --> 00:17:23,650
to learn rules from Her Majesty.

214
00:17:23,729 --> 00:17:24,930
You must not be late.

215
00:17:26,769 --> 00:17:29,370
Young Lady, wake up now.

216
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,690
