00:19:53,249 --> 00:19:54,650
Greetings as a courtesy.

252
00:19:54,850 --> 00:19:56,489
Courtesy must be detailed.

253
00:19:56,970 --> 00:19:59,170
General Ling's carriage
is waiting outside.

254
